{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Samuels fazzija us Saulu: Kapehz tu man ne effi lizzis ar Meern dusfeht/un man lizzis augſcham nahkt? Tad fazzija Sauls: Man irr fohti bail/ un tee Wilistexti karro prett manni/ un Deevs irr no man atſtabjees / un ne atbild man waits/ nedz zaur Braaveefcheem / nedz zaur Sapneem/ tapehz esmu es tew aizinajs/ ka tu man Padohmu peedohdi / ko man buhs darriht."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Samuels: Rapehz tad tu man waiza / kad tas KUNGS no tewim atſtabjees / un tew par Eenaidneeku tappis?"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS irr tew darrijs/ ko wiꞥſch zaur mann irr runnajs/ un tas KUNGS irrto Walſtibu no tawas Rohkas atrahwis/ un Dahwidam tawam Tuwakam dewis/"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz ka tu ta KUNga Balkfnei ne eſt klaufijs/un pehz winna bahrgahin Dufnahm ne darrijees prett Amaleku / tapehz irr tas KUNGS tew fchoodeen fcho Leetu darrijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS nodohs Israëlu lihds ar tewim teem Wilistereem Rohkâ / jo rihtu buhſi tu un tawi Dehli ar mañim. Un tas KUNGS dohs Israëta Lehgeri eekſch to Wilistetu Rohkas."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad kritte Sauls peepeſchi tik garſch ka wiꞥſch bija pec Semmes/ un bihjajahs fohti par Samueta Wahrdem/ ka ceekſch"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze ta Seeiva pa Saula/ un redſeja/ ka wiꞥſch tohti bij iſbhjiees/ un fazzija us winnu: Raugi / tawa Kalpone itawat Balkfnei paklaufijuti / ues efimu mannu Dſhwibu manā Rohkā lickuſi / un tawar Wahrdam paklaufijuſi/ ko tu umanni runnajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad klausi nu arri / fuosans/ tawas Kalpones Balknei/ un eszelſchu tew kahdu Kummoſti Matesß preekſcha/ un ehditad tew buhs atkaſ Spehka / ktu atkaſ warr pa Zelku eet."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet wiꞥſch leedſehs / ufazzija: Es ne gribbu ehſt / bewinna Kalpi un ta Seewa stubinaja to/ka wiꞥſch winno Balknei paklaufija. Un wiꞥſch zehlabaugſcham no Semnes / un apfehdehs us Gultu."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tai Seewai bij barohts Tetſch Sehtâ/ un winnſteidſehs/ un nokawe to / un neime Miltus/ un mihztja tohs/ uzeppe neraudſetas Kurraſchas."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un zehle to Saalamuwinna Kalpeein preekſcha / un tehde/ pehz zehlehs tee / un gahnohst tai pascha Nakti."
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
